        },
        "subject": "LU-7052 llite: free iovec with kvfree",
        "message": "LU-7052 llite: free iovec with kvfree\n\nCommit 98883bd3e2cc48a3a5674ce140ad74bece37df05 added support for\niov_iter_get_pages_alloc for newer kernels, instead of\nll_get_user_pages. However the iovec was still freed within\nll_free_user_pages, using OBD_FREE_LARGE. Use kvfree instead (like in\nthe linux kernel).\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: Id1f8cb7e0c975a50907b14c7070b9c1cf7ba556f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
